---

<div class="w-full bg-white">
	<div
		class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-16 py-12 sm:py-14 lg:py-16"
	>
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 lg:gap-8">
			<div
				class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 w-full max-w-[640px] text-center"
			>
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 w-full">
					<h1
						class="font-Inter font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] leading-tight lg:leading-[56px] text-[#030217] w-full"
					>
						Controla tu inventario, sin errores ni sorpresas
					</h1>
					<p
						class="font-Inter font-normal text-lg leading-7 text-[#030217] w-full"
					>
						Diseñado para dueños de bodegas y emprendedores que buscan reducir
						pérdidas, evitar quiebres de stock y tomar decisiones con datos
						confiables
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 w-full">
					<button
						class="bg-[#ffa22a] border-2 border-[#030217] rounded-lg px-6 py-3 shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_#030217] hover:shadow-[1px_1px_0px_0px_#030217] hover:translate-x-[1px] hover:translate-y-[1px] transition-all"
					>
						<span
							class="font-Inter font-semibold text-base text-black leading-6"
							>Prueba StockTrack gratis</span
						>
					</button>
					<p class="font-Inter font-normal text-xs leading-4 text-[#030217]">
						14 días gratis <br /> No necesitas tarjeta
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="w-full max-w-[955px] mt-2 lg:mt-4">
				<div
					class="w-full h-[300px] sm:h-[350px] lg:h-[400px] bg-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-cover bg-center flex items-center justify-center"
				>
					<div class="text-gray-500 font-Inter font-medium">
						Imagen del producto
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


